# Implementation Plan: Unified AI Layer (`agent-api`)

A separate, production-deployable Express.js server that exposes unified AI capabilities (LLM, STT, TTS, Image, Storage, Compute, HuggingFace) as x402-gated endpoints on the Stellar Testnet. All services are auto-registered in the Stellar Bazaar on startup for agent discovery.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a **separate project folder** (`agent-api/`) inside your existing repo. It will have its own `package.json`, `.env`, and `tsconfig.json`.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **API Keys Needed Before Running:**
> - `GROQ_API_KEY` — From [console.groq.com](https://console.groq.com)
> - `DEEPGRAM_API_KEY` — From [console.deepgram.com](https://console.deepgram.com) (**$200 free credits on signup**)
> - `FAL_KEY` — From [fal.ai/dashboard](https://fal.ai/dashboard) (**free credits on signup**)
> - `PINATA_JWT` — From [app.pinata.cloud](https://app.pinata.cloud)
> - `HF_ACCESS_TOKEN` — From [huggingface.co/settings/tokens](https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens) (free)
> - `STELLAR_ADDRESS` — Your Stellar Testnet address (to receive payments)

> [!NOTE]
> **Piston (Compute):** The public Piston API (`emkc.org`) now requires authorization. The plan includes a **self-hosted Docker instance** for the compute route. You need Docker installed. If you don't have Docker, this route will be skipped for the MVP and noted as `COMING_SOON`.

---

## Project Structure

```
stellar-bazar/
├── agent-api/               ← NEW: Separate project
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── server.ts        ← Main Express server + x402 middleware
│   │   ├── router.ts        ← Intelligent LLM routing logic
│   │   ├── routes/
│   │   │   ├── llm.ts       ← POST /v1/chat (Groq LLMs)
│   │   │   ├── stt.ts       ← POST /v1/stt (Deepgram Nova-3)
│   │   │   ├── tts.ts       ← POST /v1/tts (Deepgram Aura)
│   │   │   ├── image.ts     ← POST /v1/image (fal.ai Flux)
│   │   │   ├── storage.ts   ← POST /v1/storage (Pinata/IPFS)
│   │   │   ├── compute.ts   ← POST /v1/compute (Piston)
│   │   │   └── hf.ts        ← POST /v1/hf/:model_id (HuggingFace)
│   │   └── utils/
│   │       ├── pricing.ts   ← Dynamic price map per route
│   │       └── bazaar.ts    ← Auto-register all routes in Bazaar on startup
│   ├── .env
│   ├── .env.example
│   ├── package.json
│   └── tsconfig.json
```

